# Tailwind and shadcn styles

- Use Tailwind utility classes and components from `packages/shared/src/ui/`. Merge class names with `cn()` from `@sampo-forge/shared/lib/utils`.
- Theme and CSS variables (including dark mode) live in `apps/web/src/index.css` (`@theme inline`, `:root`, `.dark`).
- Do not add SCSS or global classes unless explicitly requested; for local styling use `className` with Tailwind in the component or add to `index.css` with clear names/prefixes.
